        "content": "Ground the request only to the admitted identifiers below. Select semantic goals, explicit exclusions, trust policy, and artifact contract. Do not copy dependencies, assign providers, decide feasibility, or create a plan. Use null for an omitted policy or contract so deterministic defaults can apply.\nRules:\n1. Read depends_on before choosing goals. Select terminal requested outcomes only; prerequisites are added deterministically. If C depends on B and B depends on A, a request to perform A, B, then C has only C as a goal.\n2. A term matching a capability, policy, contract, agent name, description, or alias is resolved and must not appear in unresolved_terms.\n3. Use ambiguous when the request says either, unspecified, unclear, not specified, or otherwise leaves incompatible meanings unresolved. Put only the unresolved phrase from the request in unresolved_terms. Never put unused catalog identifiers or distractors in unresolved_terms.\n4. Add forbidden identifiers only for explicit prohibitions such as 'do not use'. Never infer a prohibition from provider capabilities or availability.\n5. Return only the schema-conforming JSON object and no explanation."
      },
      {
        "role": "user",
        "content": "CAPABILITIES\n- v07-p18-deliver: Publish sensor inspection verified brief; Release the checked final brief for sensor inspection.; aliases=['issue sensor inspection brief', 'release sensor inspection summary', 'issue the brief']; depends_on=['v07-p18-verify']\n- v07-p18-archive: Archive sensor inspection verified brief; Preserve the checked sensor inspection brief for long-term retention.; aliases=['retain sensor inspection brief', 'store sensor inspection summary', 'retain the brief']; depends_on=['v07-p18-verify']\n- v07-p18-verify: Validate sensor inspection source packet; Check the assembled sensor inspection material for correctness.; aliases=['check sensor inspection inputs', 'verify sensor inspection packet', 'check the packet']; depends_on=['v07-p18-prepare']\n- v07-p18-prepare: Assemble sensor inspection source packet; Collect the source material needed for sensor inspection.; aliases=['gather sensor inspection inputs', 'prepare sensor inspection packet', 'gather the inputs', 'prepare the sensor inspection packet']; depends_on=[]\n\nTRUST POLICIES\n- v07-p18-ordinary: ordinary sensor inspection assurance; Standard trust is sufficient for this sensor inspection request.; aliases=['normal sensor inspection assurance']\n- v07-p18-elevated: elevated sensor inspection assurance; Elevated trust is mandatory for this sensor inspection request.; aliases=['high assurance for sensor inspection']\n\nARTIFACT CONTRACTS\n- v07-p18-json: sensor inspection machine-readable JSON; Return the final sensor inspection result as JSON.; aliases=['sensor inspection json output']\n- v07-p18-signed-pdf: sensor inspection signed PDF; Return the final sensor inspection result as a signed PDF.; aliases=['signed sensor inspection document']\n\nAGENTS\n- v07-p18-preparer: sensor inspection source preparer\n- v07-p18-verifier: sensor inspection source verifier\n- v07-p18-primary: primary sensor inspection publisher\n- v07-p18-backup: backup sensor inspection publisher\n\nREQUEST\nFor this sensor inspection job, gather the inputs, check the packet, and issue the brief with normal sensor inspection assurance as sensor inspection JSON output."
